        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="gkYjlXACWcnSYZTp3MUz-25" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=none;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="190" x="305" y="1820" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="gkYjlXACWcnSYZTp3MUz-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Functional Requirements&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1w1i6fe&quot; data-start=&quot;255&quot; data-end=&quot;279&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1w1i6fe&quot; data-start=&quot;255&quot; data-end=&quot;279&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;1. Limit Requests&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;280&quot; data-end=&quot;382&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;67i7k&quot; data-start=&quot;280&quot; data-end=&quot;345&quot;&gt;System should restrict number of requests per user/IP/API key&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;6c7ayo&quot; data-start=&quot;346&quot; data-end=&quot;382&quot;&gt;Example: &lt;em data-start=&quot;357&quot; data-end=&quot;382&quot;&gt;100 requests per minute&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;9i1ve&quot; data-start=&quot;389&quot; data-end=&quot;418&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;2. Identify the Client&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;419&quot; data-end=&quot;512&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;2brnbc&quot; data-start=&quot;419&quot; data-end=&quot;512&quot;&gt;Each request must be identifiable using:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;464&quot; data-end=&quot;512&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ofu2za&quot; data-start=&quot;464&quot; data-end=&quot;478&quot;&gt;user_id OR&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1pb1cey&quot; data-start=&quot;481&quot; data-end=&quot;498&quot;&gt;IP address OR&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;10bg8zr&quot; data-start=&quot;501&quot; data-end=&quot;512&quot;&gt;API key&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1r7zd0k&quot; data-start=&quot;519&quot; data-end=&quot;552&quot;&gt;3. Allow / Reject Requests&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;553&quot; data-end=&quot;625&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;6p2q5k&quot; data-start=&quot;553&quot; data-end=&quot;590&quot;&gt;If within limit → allow request&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1hkc00s&quot; data-start=&quot;591&quot; data-end=&quot;625&quot;&gt;If exceeded → reject request&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;627&quot; data-end=&quot;637&quot;&gt;Return:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;638&quot; data-end=&quot;670&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;cyp5nm&quot; data-start=&quot;638&quot; data-end=&quot;670&quot;&gt;HTTP &lt;strong data-start=&quot;645&quot; data-end=&quot;670&quot;&gt;429 Too Many Requests&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;19kmsuy&quot; data-start=&quot;677&quot; data-end=&quot;709&quot;&gt;4. Support Multiple Rules&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;710&quot; data-end=&quot;847&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;g0n30j&quot; data-start=&quot;710&quot; data-end=&quot;847&quot;&gt;Different limits for different cases:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;752&quot; data-end=&quot;847&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1kskfii&quot; data-start=&quot;752&quot; data-end=&quot;779&quot;&gt;Free users → 50 req/min&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1dtkqz9&quot; data-start=&quot;782&quot; data-end=&quot;813&quot;&gt;Premium users → 500 req/min&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1fg0fgb&quot; data-start=&quot;816&quot; data-end=&quot;847&quot;&gt;Login API → stricter limits&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;of292u&quot; data-start=&quot;854&quot; data-end=&quot;881&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;5. Time-based Limits&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;971&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1d3hs0z&quot; data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;971&quot;&gt;Support rate limits over time windows:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;925&quot; data-end=&quot;971&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;93w8bj&quot; data-start=&quot;925&quot; data-end=&quot;939&quot;&gt;Per second&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ezwns1&quot; data-start=&quot;942&quot; data-end=&quot;956&quot;&gt;Per minute&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;of6d7z&quot; data-start=&quot;959&quot; data-end=&quot;971&quot;&gt;Per hour&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;13yzbob&quot; data-start=&quot;978&quot; data-end=&quot;1007&quot;&gt;6. Configurable Limits&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1008&quot; data-end=&quot;1089&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;56bq7u&quot; data-start=&quot;1008&quot; data-end=&quot;1089&quot;&gt;Admin should be able to:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1037&quot; data-end=&quot;1089&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;zk3wv9&quot; data-start=&quot;1037&quot; data-end=&quot;1066&quot;&gt;Change limits dynamically&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ekefbx&quot; data-start=&quot;1069&quot; data-end=&quot;1089&quot;&gt;Add/remove rules&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;l3gqp&quot; data-start=&quot;1096&quot; data-end=&quot;1122&quot;&gt;7. Provide Feedback&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1123&quot; data-end=&quot;1197&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1oslej2&quot; data-start=&quot;1123&quot; data-end=&quot;1197&quot;&gt;Response should include:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1152&quot; data-end=&quot;1197&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1s0hq1i&quot; data-start=&quot;1152&quot; data-end=&quot;1174&quot;&gt;Remaining requests&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1u0chx8&quot; data-start=&quot;1177&quot; data-end=&quot;1197&quot;&gt;Retry-after time&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="840" width="440" x="30" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="gkYjlXACWcnSYZTp3MUz-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Non-Functional Requirements&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1w1i6fe&quot; data-start=&quot;255&quot; data-end=&quot;279&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;11saxwq&quot; data-start=&quot;1297&quot; data-end=&quot;1325&quot;&gt;1. High Performance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1326&quot; data-end=&quot;1427&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1kd10la&quot; data-start=&quot;1326&quot; data-end=&quot;1373&quot;&gt;Decision must be &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1345&quot; data-end=&quot;1373&quot;&gt;very fast (&amp;lt;5ms ideally)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;172ncny&quot; data-start=&quot;1374&quot; data-end=&quot;1427&quot;&gt;Because every request passes through rate limiter&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;9i1ve&quot; data-start=&quot;389&quot; data-end=&quot;418&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;2. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;High Scalability&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1464&quot; data-end=&quot;1543&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;13dqfhw&quot; data-start=&quot;1464&quot; data-end=&quot;1543&quot;&gt;Should handle:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1483&quot; data-end=&quot;1543&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;q6dw9o&quot; data-start=&quot;1483&quot; data-end=&quot;1504&quot;&gt;Millions of users&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1pxl6e1&quot; data-start=&quot;1507&quot; data-end=&quot;1543&quot;&gt;Thousands of requests per second&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1hotgxp&quot; data-start=&quot;1550&quot; data-end=&quot;1574&quot;&gt;3. Low Latency&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1r7zd0k&quot; data-start=&quot;519&quot; data-end=&quot;552&quot;&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1575&quot; data-end=&quot;1631&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;odf6fq&quot; data-start=&quot;1575&quot; data-end=&quot;1631&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Rate limiting should not slow down API significantly&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1tuj7yw&quot; data-start=&quot;1638&quot; data-end=&quot;1668&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;4. High Availability&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;19kmsuy&quot; data-start=&quot;677&quot; data-end=&quot;709&quot;&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1669&quot; data-end=&quot;1777&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1sfpf8r&quot; data-start=&quot;1669&quot; data-end=&quot;1706&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;System should always be available&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;16dcycn&quot; data-start=&quot;1707&quot; data-end=&quot;1777&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;If rate limiter fails → system should still work (graceful fallback)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;lk1rg&quot; data-start=&quot;1784&quot; data-end=&quot;1823&quot;&gt;5. Distributed System Support&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;of292u&quot; data-start=&quot;854&quot; data-end=&quot;881&quot;&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1824&quot; data-end=&quot;1906&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;149fum1&quot; data-start=&quot;1824&quot; data-end=&quot;1863&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Should work across multiple servers&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1vdpa5v&quot; data-start=&quot;1864&quot; data-end=&quot;1906&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Counters must be shared (not local only)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;ltwqih&quot; data-start=&quot;1913&quot; data-end=&quot;1961&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;6&lt;/font&gt;. Consistency vs Performance Tradeoff&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;13yzbob&quot; data-start=&quot;978&quot; data-end=&quot;1007&quot;&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1962&quot; data-end=&quot;2052&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;19pdgti&quot; data-start=&quot;1962&quot; data-end=&quot;1997&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Slight inconsistency acceptable&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ds508s&quot; data-start=&quot;1998&quot; data-end=&quot;2052&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Performance is more important than strict accuracy&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;n87txc&quot; data-start=&quot;2059&quot; data-end=&quot;2087&quot;&gt;7. Fault Tolerance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;l3gqp&quot; data-start=&quot;1096&quot; data-end=&quot;1122&quot;&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;2088&quot; data-end=&quot;2136&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;b92com&quot; data-start=&quot;2088&quot; data-end=&quot;2136&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;If one node fails → system continues working&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;199acws&quot; data-start=&quot;2143&quot; data-end=&quot;2173&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;8&lt;/font&gt;. Memory Efficiency&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;l3gqp&quot; data-start=&quot;1096&quot; data-end=&quot;1122&quot;&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;2174&quot; data-end=&quot;2260&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;zad88y&quot; data-start=&quot;2174&quot; data-end=&quot;2217&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Should not store unlimited request logs&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;jnrjj1&quot; data-start=&quot;2218&quot; data-end=&quot;2260&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Use optimized structures (like counters)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;9cc6a6&quot; data-start=&quot;2267&quot; data-end=&quot;2288&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;9. Security&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;l3gqp&quot; data-start=&quot;1096&quot; data-end=&quot;1122&quot;&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;2289&quot; data-end=&quot;2330&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;popoid&quot; data-start=&quot;2289&quot; data-end=&quot;2313&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Prevent abuse / DDoS&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;5b6w&quot; data-start=&quot;2314&quot; data-end=&quot;2330&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Protect APIs&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
